"section":8,"text":"The key here is the renal biopsy showing autoantibodies to basement membranes.","dimension":2,"group":7,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.050231,0.096671,0.10693,0.10635,0.10017,0.093481,0.089459,0.083418,0.079608,0.073313,0.063982,0.056394],"unified_progress":[0.048769,0.083269,0.095155,0.1033,0.10478,0.099673,0.1021,0.08923,0.083683,0.074762,0.064123,0.051162]},{"section":9,"text":"Hmm, autoantibodies against basement membranes... that makes me think of Goodpasture syndrome.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.050405,0.089563,0.10242,0.10619,0.10202,0.093017,0.089776,0.083436,0.076191,0.079173,0.065025,0.062786],"unified_progress":[0.05697,0.071521,0.085644,0.097183,0.098149,0.099525,0.097343,0.092925,0.086473,0.085304,0.071114,0.057848]},{"section":10,"text":"Wait, but sometimes that's part of a broader category.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.32905,0.053852,0.053672,0.062848,0.063177,0.064181,0.060169,0.067218,0.068348,0.06311,0.066135,0.048236],"unified_progress":[0.21949,0.085474,0.064686,0.064671,0.073997,0.07319,0.094712,0.079246,0.075899,0.060698,0.056175,0.05176]},{"section":11,"text":"Let me recall: Goodpasture's is specifically anti-GBM (glomerular basement membrane) antibodies, which can affect both the kidneys and lungs.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.052133,0.11101,0.059123,0.10437,0.10791,0.10673,0.099291,0.088854,0.078864,0.073025,0.063574,0.055118],"unified_progress":[0.055596,0.07539,0.062766,0.10255,0.1045,0.10735,0.10049,0.099379,0.091789,0.084108,0.066345,0.049734]},{"section":12,"text":"The presentation with hemoptysis and pulmonary hemorrhage along with rapidly progressive glomerulonephritis fits.","dimension":9,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.03775,0.076696,0.08593,0.092288,0.098396,0.10047,0.1006,0.094825,0.087621,0.086045,0.073802,0.065576],"unified_progress":[0.038614,0.063983,0.078509,0.087954,0.094366,0.10386,0.099904,0.099222,0.096759,0.092069,0.080647,0.064112]},{"section":13,"text":"The CXR infiltrates could be from alveolar hemorrhage.","dimension":5,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.034187,0.074614,0.085841,0.093059,0.095563,0.098883,0.099231,0.094131,0.096988,0.084165,0.07626,0.067077],"unified_progress":[0.036855,0.064431,0.08031,0.091788,0.09901,0.10173,0.099803,0.09672,0.099324,0.088522,0.07791,0.063601]},{"section":14,"text":"The elevated creatinine and urine findings (hematuria, proteinuria) point to kidney involvement.","dimension":9,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.031359,0.068083,0.08122,0.089281,0.094237,0.097101,0.10067,0.09762,0.095147,0.089449,0.084287,0.071543],"unified_progress":[0.035975,0.062368,0.076074,0.083851,0.093687,0.096384,0.099745,0.098592,0.098795,0.095231,0.088204,0.071092]},{"section":15,"text":"But wait, there's also another condition called diffuse alveolar hemorrhage syndrome, but that's a symptom rather than a diagnosis.","dimension":0,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.032599,0.065597,0.078336,0.087395,0.093641,0.095841,0.09898,0.09866,0.095297,0.095291,0.084867,0.073496],"unified_progress":[0.040828,0.061931,0.076914,0.088054,0.093367,0.097223,0.098942,0.10017,0.097095,0.096629,0.083712,0.065131]},{"section":16,"text":"The presence of anti-basement membrane antibodies on biopsy is a big clue.","dimension":2,"group":7,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.033701,0.070767,0.085376,0.091914,0.093717,0.093667,0.095253,0.092418,0.092089,0.08962,0.083199,0.078279],"unified_progress":[0.036869,0.065752,0.080783,0.090818,0.095957,0.097966,0.097742,0.095394,0.094349,0.089798,0.082834,0.071741]},{"section":17,"text":"Goodpasture's is the classic here.","dimension":7,"group":0,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.027807,0.057822,0.072235,0.081382,0.087139,0.089126,0.09248,0.092082,0.092242,0.095668,0.094122,0.11789],"unified_progress":[0.033285,0.050033,0.061208,0.071772,0.076192,0.085603,0.086368,0.093166,0.096618,0.1009,0.11349,0.13136]},{"section":18,"text":"However, sometimes anti-GBM and GPA (granulomatosis with polyangiitis) can present similarly.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.027918,0.059439,0.073799,0.087664,0.097882,0.10185,0.10443,0.099945,0.093459,0.096639,0.081458,0.075523],"unified_progress":[0.032341,0.052883,0.072563,0.084048,0.092711,0.10207,0.10296,0.10464,0.10218,0.099181,0.084876,0.069554]},{"section":19,"text":"But in GPA, you might see granulomas and necrosis, and maybe other findings like sinus issues or ear/nose involvement.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.021222,0.053822,0.07008,0.082362,0.091427,0.098466,0.10619,0.107,0.10587,0.10293,0.093216,0.067416],"unified_progress":[0.025569,0.053787,0.071898,0.082897,0.094337,0.098896,0.1031,0.10835,0.10775,0.11387,0.085359,0.054187]},{"section":20,"text":"The biopsy here mentions autoantibodies, not histological features of vasculitis with granulomas.","dimension":5,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.027947,0.063988,0.077624,0.086494,0.091431,0.096081,0.10015,0.099321,0.10206,0.094645,0.087093,0.073176],"unified_progress":[0.031582,0.062287,0.079152,0.089827,0.097744,0.10079,0.10106,0.10109,0.10176,0.094351,0.080433,0.059922]},{"section":21,"text":"Also, the anti-GBM antibodies are specific to that syndrome.","dimension":2,"group":7,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.03017,0.064218,0.078854,0.087265,0.092355,0.094031,0.097045,0.0958,0.094543,0.093571,0.087792,0.084356],"unified_progress":[0.043007,0.063191,0.076673,0.086077,0.091514,0.09557,0.096983,0.095591,0.093813,0.091343,0.086864,0.079374]},{"section":22,"text":"The combination of pulmonary and renal involvement (the so-called \"rapidly progressive glomerulonephritis plus pulmonary hemorrhage\") is classic for Goodpasture.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.028257,0.059092,0.071579,0.08319,0.09241,0.097485,0.10112,0.098549,0.096127,0.096856,0.089312,0.08602],"unified_progress":[0.035917,0.054228,0.071719,0.081904,0.08977,0.10042,0.098809,0.10043,0.099483,0.096972,0.089808,0.080536]},{"section":23,"text":"The elevated creatinine and the biopsy findings support that.","dimension":4,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.024579,0.056094,0.071719,0.081131,0.088301,0.09281,0.098297,0.098594,0.10122,0.099604,0.099235,0.088419],"unified_progress":[0.044251,0.056975,0.069395,0.078891,0.087947,0.095177,0.095952,0.09808,0.10013,0.099682,0.094744,0.078781]},{"section":24,"text":"So I think the most likely diagnosis is Goodpasture syndrome.","dimension":7,"group":0,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.020203,0.040576,0.05048,0.058306,0.066578,0.073959,0.082334,0.088981,0.098973,0.10499,0.12256,0.19206],"unified_progress":[0.020979,0.030564,0.038885,0.048563,0.053821,0.068878,0.073058,0.090107,0.10432,0.11273,0.15288,0.20521]}]}}